        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Have we figured out what we want from `vim.pack` with this? I was debating giving it a shot to implement a PR for this, but am unsure about what we would want for some of the actions\n\n- `vim.pack.add('~/my-plugins/plugin1')` symlinks it to \n   `vim.fs.joinpath(vim.fn.stdpath(\"data\"), \"site\", \"pack\", \"core\", \"opt\", \"plugin1\")`\n- `vim.pack.del({ \"plugin1\" })` removes the symlink\n- `vim.pack.update` ??\n- `vim.pack.get()` resolves the original path, and tries to resolve version using git (?)",
